data.description: 2/1 BUY DOWN OPTION AVAILABLE! BEDROOM/BATH DOWNSTAIRS, NEWER KITCHEN, QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS, FRESH PAINT, LARGE BACKYARD, LAMINATE HARDWOOD FLOORS, STAINLESS UPGRADED APPLIANCES, CUSTOM BLINDS, SOLAR, SMART HOME FEATURES, LARGE LOFT WITH VIEW! Nestled within the highly desirable Audi Murphy Ranch community, you'll relish the convenience of exceptional schools, local shopping, dining, and recreation facilities. This location perfectly balances a tranquil residential atmosphere with easy access to all essential amenities. Step into your new sanctuary. The entire interior has been freshly painted, creating a bright and inviting ambiance. Blinds adorn every window, offering privacy and light control. Laminate hardwood through out will not go unnoticed. This exquisite home that embodies the perfect harmony of modern living and comfort, top-notch upgrades and ample space to make cherished memories. The centerpiece of this home is its gourmet kitchen, a chef's dream come true. Modern appliances, quartz countertops, and ample storage ensure that it's well-equipped for hosting elegant dinners or crafting delicious family meals. This culinary haven features modern appliances, sleek countertops, and abundant storage, ensuring it's ready for hosting elegant dinners or creating delicious family meals. The living room, generously proportioned and bathed in natural light, is the ideal backdrop for quality family time and entertaining. The open layout is designed to facilitate both cozy gatherings. Your new home boasts a wealth of upgraded amenities, including gorgeous laminate flooring that's not only a visual delight but also easy to maintain. Solar panels have been thoughtfully installed to keep energy costs in check. Upstairs, you'll discover a massive loft, providing a flexible space that can be tailored to your needs. Whether it becomes a home office, a play area, or a cozy reading nook, this loft is the icing on the cake. The master bedroom suite is more than adequate, while the downstairs bedroom and full bath is a guest or family members dream. Stepping outside, you'll discover a generous backyard retreat. Recently adorned with freshly laid sod, it provides a fresh and welcoming green landscape, perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply basking in the California sun. Here you can craft your personal outdoor oasis. This home is a rare find, with its upgraded kitchen, spacious living area, and contemporary amenities. Seize the opportunity to make it yours.
